org.hibernate.ogm.model.key.spi

Class IdSourceKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.model.key.spi.IdSourceKey

  • public final class IdSourceKey
extends Object
    Represents a source of an id sequence such as a table (row) or a physical sequence. This is used to identify a Sequence or a Table based id generator. At most a single column is needed: columnName and columnValue to map to the attributes of JPA's TableGenerated.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling, Sanne Grinovero
